WEBVTT

01:00.560 --> 01:01.603
You came.

01:02.729 --> 01:03.897
You told me to.

01:09.527 --> 01:11.696
EPISODE 5

01:15.700 --> 01:17.786
I missed you so much.

01:18.620 --> 01:19.746
So did I.

01:23.458 --> 01:24.542
Let's go in.

01:34.010 --> 01:35.053
Do you want some coffee?

01:35.595 --> 01:36.429
Sure.

01:44.437 --> 01:46.397
Why are you acting
like you've never been here?

01:48.191 --> 01:49.275
I know, right?

01:51.945 --> 01:53.571
Just make yourself at home.

01:55.365 --> 01:56.324
Shall I?

02:01.454 --> 02:04.249
Bring me a good cup of coffee.

02:06.751 --> 02:08.002
Well, don't get too comfortable.

02:16.469 --> 02:17.804
You're doubting again, aren't you?

02:18.680 --> 02:20.014
"Can I really be doing this?"

02:22.976 --> 02:26.813
I closed my eyes
while walking down the hall

02:27.021 --> 02:28.565
so that I won't see Gyeong-seon's place.

02:29.649 --> 02:30.775
Gosh.

02:34.112 --> 02:37.031
Do you know what this reminds me of?

02:37.866 --> 02:41.536
You know how kids
invite their friends over

02:41.619 --> 02:45.123
when their parents aren't home
and do things

02:45.206 --> 02:46.541
that they're not supposed to do.

02:49.794 --> 02:50.920
You mean things like this?

02:51.588 --> 02:52.755
You startled me.

03:09.856 --> 03:11.024
Seung-ho!

03:14.360 --> 03:16.237
Is Jin-a working again today?

03:17.447 --> 03:19.490
Who knows? She's not the type

03:19.574 --> 03:21.993
to tell me what she is up to.

03:22.869 --> 03:25.747
You didn't even eat breakfast today.
Have rice if you don't want noodles.

03:25.830 --> 03:29.042
- It doesn't matter.
- Why doesn't it matter?

03:29.125 --> 03:31.753
You should eat what you like more.

03:31.836 --> 03:34.964
You're the pillar of the family
and the only child that makes me proud.

03:37.133 --> 03:39.886
Let's go shopping after this meal.

03:40.345 --> 03:43.306
I'll buy you some clothes, shoes,
and other things you need--

03:43.389 --> 03:44.891
I want to go over to Jun-hui's place.

03:45.975 --> 03:48.019
Why? You guys will just play games again.

03:48.102 --> 03:50.230
It's not like that helps you study.

03:50.647 --> 03:52.315
Mom, you just don't know.

03:52.398 --> 03:54.567
You have to be smart to play those games.

03:54.901 --> 03:56.986
And Jun-hui makes those games.

03:57.862 --> 04:00.657
Why did he go to art school
if he's that smart?

04:01.115 --> 04:02.867
What nonsense are you talking about?

04:02.951 --> 04:05.536
I'm just saying no matter how smart he is,

04:05.620 --> 04:07.455
you are in a different league from him.

04:11.167 --> 04:13.878
You two have been friends
since you were kids,

04:13.962 --> 04:16.214
so I won't tell you
to distance yourself from him,

04:16.589 --> 04:18.800
but from now on,
you should try to befriend only those

04:18.883 --> 04:21.636
who can benefit you in the future.

04:21.719 --> 04:23.221
I just don't want you to struggle.

04:23.304 --> 04:25.807
You need to be prepared
in advance so that--

04:26.224 --> 04:27.350
I'm done.

04:29.060 --> 04:30.895
You didn't even finish your food!

04:33.481 --> 04:34.816
What's the matter with you?

04:41.322 --> 04:44.075
You may not want to hear
these things right now,

04:44.450 --> 04:47.578
but you'll eventually come to realize
that everything I said was right.

05:11.477 --> 05:12.395
My gosh!

05:13.396 --> 05:14.605
It's Gyeong-seon.

05:15.356 --> 05:17.066
Can't you just ignore it?

05:17.525 --> 05:19.027
This is the second time she's calling.

06:21.130 --> 06:23.299
What were you up to?

06:23.382 --> 06:25.718
Oh, I was on the phone
with one of my co-workers.

06:25.802 --> 06:27.678
I see. I wanted to show you the sea.

06:29.222 --> 06:31.140
Ta-da!

06:31.766 --> 06:32.850
Isn't it amazing?

06:32.934 --> 06:34.852
Yes, what a breathtaking view.

06:36.187 --> 06:38.564
Did something happen? You seem down.

06:39.899 --> 06:43.611
No, nothing happened.
I'm just jealous that you're there.

06:43.694 --> 06:46.614
We should've come together.
This was organized by your company anyway.

06:46.697 --> 06:47.824
Totally.

06:48.950 --> 06:50.868
It looks like you're outside.
Where are you now?

06:51.077 --> 06:52.912
It looks familiar for some reason.

06:53.162 --> 06:56.415
Oh, I'm meeting someone here.

06:56.499 --> 06:59.085
It's a park near the office.

06:59.168 --> 07:00.753
What? Are you meeting a guy?

07:00.837 --> 07:02.797
Unfortunately, no.

07:02.880 --> 07:05.216
- Obviously. I shouldn't even have asked.
- Exactly.

07:05.299 --> 07:08.845
I'm only away for a day,
so don't cry while I'm gone, okay?

07:09.720 --> 07:10.972
Okay, Gyeong-seon.

07:11.264 --> 07:13.099
- Let's talk soon.
- All right.

07:38.249 --> 07:39.250
What's wrong?

07:40.168 --> 07:41.127
I...

07:42.044 --> 07:43.671
I have to use the bathroom.

07:43.754 --> 07:44.589
Welcome back.

08:00.271 --> 08:02.315
How can he be so nonchalant about it?

08:05.568 --> 08:07.778
He's pretending to be,
but he must be very nervous.

08:08.863 --> 08:13.117
The woman seems so nervous
that she doesn't know where to look

08:13.201 --> 08:14.952
or where to place her hands.

08:15.036 --> 08:16.204
But he isn't like that.

08:16.621 --> 08:18.206
It seems like she's the only one in love.

08:19.832 --> 08:22.210
If he shows that he is nervous,
the woman might feel anxious.

08:22.293 --> 08:23.711
So he's hiding his emotions.

08:24.504 --> 08:27.256
How would she know how he feels
about her if he doesn't say it out loud?

08:29.634 --> 08:30.927
I'm sure he wants to do so.

08:31.677 --> 08:32.678
But...

08:36.432 --> 08:37.433
But what?

08:39.435 --> 08:41.062
Words can't describe everything.

08:46.192 --> 08:48.611
You're beginning to worry, aren't you?

08:51.989 --> 08:53.991
This is why I don't say it out loud.

08:54.200 --> 08:55.910
No matter how many times I say it,

08:56.077 --> 08:58.371
you don't believe what I say
and ask me over and over again.

08:59.914 --> 09:01.457
You should listen to me more.

09:04.752 --> 09:06.671
"You should listen to me more"?

09:07.129 --> 09:09.924
You're being cheeky. I'm older than you.

09:10.841 --> 09:11.968
You're my girlfriend.

09:15.304 --> 09:17.223
You always point things out.

09:18.266 --> 09:19.976
I'm telling the truth.

09:20.351 --> 09:23.229
Why? Do you want me to be
just your friend's little brother again?

09:32.947 --> 09:34.115
Look at me.

09:35.283 --> 09:37.118
No. I want to watch the movie.

09:38.953 --> 09:40.663
I want to watch you.

09:46.877 --> 09:48.004
I want to hold you.

09:51.799 --> 09:53.593
I want to hold you closer, Jin-a.

12:51.645 --> 12:53.022
It's unreal

12:53.939 --> 12:56.025
that such a pretty lady
is right in front of me.

13:00.154 --> 13:01.405
It feels real now, right?

13:03.324 --> 13:05.451
Why can't you be serious for five minutes?

13:06.494 --> 13:08.621
It's because I feel shy.

13:11.081 --> 13:12.249
What are you shy about?

13:13.167 --> 13:14.335
Aren't we past that stage?

13:15.127 --> 13:16.712
Why you...

13:21.842 --> 13:23.093
Can't you stay here tonight?

13:37.483 --> 13:39.360
Mom, you should sleep in the bed.

13:39.944 --> 13:42.655
Dad, you too. Don't sleep on the couch.

13:43.697 --> 13:45.616
My goodness, I dozed off.

13:46.450 --> 13:49.328
No, I wasn't sleeping.

13:52.957 --> 13:55.292
How about some beer with your dad?

13:55.376 --> 13:58.379
No, don't make mom scold you.
You should go to bed.

13:58.462 --> 14:01.674
I'm not going to scold you. Go ahead.

14:01.757 --> 14:03.926
No. I'll gain weight
if I drink late at night.

14:04.176 --> 14:07.054
If you knew that much, how did drinking
at night become your daily routine?

14:07.638 --> 14:09.348
Whatever.

14:09.431 --> 14:11.767
You can drown yourselves in alcohol.
I don't care.

14:13.102 --> 14:15.229
I'm going to sleep.

15:51.659 --> 15:52.576
I give up.

16:02.878 --> 16:04.171
I ran out of options.

16:06.006 --> 16:07.049
I'm screwed.

16:12.596 --> 16:15.140
Hey, that's cheating.

16:15.224 --> 16:16.350
- Give it back.
- What...

16:16.433 --> 16:17.267
Hold on, I'll...

16:17.351 --> 16:18.852
What's wrong?

16:25.526 --> 16:26.360
Here it is.

16:26.777 --> 16:27.861
Call the game off.

16:27.945 --> 16:29.947
This never happened.

18:25.312 --> 18:26.688
We're here.

18:54.007 --> 18:55.300
I'll go now.

19:02.850 --> 19:03.892
Bye.

19:14.194 --> 19:15.612
Now I really have to go.

19:18.615 --> 19:19.783
You deserve that.

19:21.869 --> 19:23.036
See you.

19:25.038 --> 19:25.998
Bye.

19:34.631 --> 19:36.675
Go on. See you.

19:36.842 --> 19:37.926
Bye.

19:42.639 --> 19:43.682
Bye.

19:51.899 --> 19:52.983
Bye.

19:53.942 --> 19:55.319
Go on.

20:39.863 --> 20:41.573
Dad, are you up already?

20:41.657 --> 20:43.242
Yes. Were you outside?

20:43.325 --> 20:46.286
Yes. I worked out.

20:46.495 --> 20:47.537
You worked out?

20:47.621 --> 20:50.374
Yes, I haven't been
feeling well these days.

20:50.874 --> 20:52.960
And I couldn't fall back asleep
after I woke up.

20:53.043 --> 20:54.461
So I went outside for a walk.

20:54.544 --> 20:57.339
Next time, go out when it's bright
or take me with you.

20:57.506 --> 21:00.300
I didn't go anywhere far.
I took a walk nearby.

21:00.384 --> 21:01.593
- I'll go inside now.
- Okay.

21:10.686 --> 21:12.854
- Hello.
- Good morning.

21:12.938 --> 21:14.940
- Long time no see.
- Jin-a.

21:21.613 --> 21:22.864
- Come on. Give me five.
- What?

21:22.948 --> 21:23.865
Give me five.

21:24.783 --> 21:25.826
I'm proud of you.

21:26.994 --> 21:29.705
- What was that about?
- I heard you screwed Mr. Kong over.

21:31.957 --> 21:34.251
I didn't screw him over.

21:34.751 --> 21:36.878
Then what was it?
You rarely back out of such things.

21:38.255 --> 21:41.633
What kind of person
did you guys think I was until now?

21:42.217 --> 21:44.094
- A loyal servant.
- It's more like a loyal servant

21:44.177 --> 21:45.721
who makes others look bad.

21:47.389 --> 21:49.766
I'm just saying you did a good job.

21:49.850 --> 21:51.518
I'm glad you're one of us now.

21:51.601 --> 21:53.395
It's as if she just joined
a secret society.

21:53.478 --> 21:56.231
Just know that you'll never
be able to join, Dong-u.

21:56.440 --> 21:57.858
I don't even want to.

21:58.066 --> 21:59.234
I want to join.

21:59.318 --> 22:01.069
I have no intention to join,
but good luck.

22:13.623 --> 22:14.624
Ms. Yoon.

22:15.751 --> 22:16.710
Follow me.

22:34.603 --> 22:35.604
What?

22:48.909 --> 22:50.744
That's very unlike of "Ms. Tambourine."

22:51.745 --> 22:54.247
- She's like a different person.
- I know.

22:58.668 --> 23:01.004
They aren't just anyone, you know.

23:02.047 --> 23:03.882
They are my relatives.

23:05.050 --> 23:07.302
How am I going to face them now?

23:08.595 --> 23:13.100
You can't just get away with this
with a simple apology. Do you understand?

23:15.811 --> 23:18.563
I never apologized, sir.

23:22.317 --> 23:23.360
Mr. Nam.

23:24.194 --> 23:27.322
I am not exactly sure what I did wrong.

23:27.864 --> 23:31.368
I took care of every single task
I had to take care of at the store.

23:32.035 --> 23:33.954
Can you be more specific

23:34.037 --> 23:36.289
about what I did wrong?

23:40.794 --> 23:42.671
That's not what he's talking about.

23:43.171 --> 23:44.631
Stop acting like you don't get it.

23:45.882 --> 23:49.761
I'm just telling you that I did
what I had to do as a supervisor.

23:50.303 --> 23:53.932
Anything else that's not related to that
isn't what I'm required to do.

23:56.643 --> 23:59.938
Mr. Nam, is it wrong for me
to think this way?

24:02.524 --> 24:03.483
Well...

24:04.025 --> 24:05.193
As for your job...

24:05.694 --> 24:07.237
Well, I never said you were wrong.

24:08.864 --> 24:12.325
I'm just saying that there are times
when you have to...

24:13.952 --> 24:16.204
Mr. Kong, why did you

24:16.913 --> 24:18.248
deal with it that way?

24:18.748 --> 24:19.624
You're not an amateur.

24:21.168 --> 24:24.129
You could've just had drinks
with them over lunch.

24:24.462 --> 24:26.131
Why did you have to make it
into a big deal?

24:27.841 --> 24:28.967
I'm sorry, sir.

24:37.350 --> 24:38.351
Hey.

24:39.060 --> 24:42.314
Hitting on a girl sounds easy to do.

24:43.356 --> 24:46.067
But no woman would just say yes to me

24:46.276 --> 24:48.195
when I ask her out for a meal.

24:48.945 --> 24:50.655
Then ask her to buy you a meal.

24:50.906 --> 24:53.617
I don't even know
if she'll eat with me even if I buy.

24:53.700 --> 24:57.037
So she'll definitely think it's a turnoff
if I ask her to buy.

24:58.330 --> 24:59.748
It worked for me.

25:00.707 --> 25:02.584
Gosh, you're being arrogant again.

25:06.046 --> 25:08.715
Hey, come on.

25:09.341 --> 25:11.885
Can you please try to hook me up with...

25:13.428 --> 25:14.387
It's Ms. Yoon.

25:27.067 --> 25:29.319
- You should go first.
- What are you...

25:31.196 --> 25:34.449
I know she's your friend,
but don't meddle with her work.

25:35.450 --> 25:36.701
I know that much.

25:37.953 --> 25:40.205
You're such a troublemaker.

25:41.164 --> 25:42.165
See you.

25:47.879 --> 25:50.215
Don't just stand there and talk to me.

25:51.967 --> 25:53.176
What's your problem?

25:57.597 --> 25:59.849
Excuse me. Can I borrow a lighter?

26:00.767 --> 26:02.894
Sorry, I don't smoke.

26:03.561 --> 26:04.688
Oh, really?

26:05.730 --> 26:08.650
Come to think of it,
I'm trying to quit myself.

26:12.195 --> 26:14.948
Hey, it is you. What are you doing here?

26:18.493 --> 26:20.870
Well, anyway...

26:21.454 --> 26:23.248
Let's do better next time, okay?

26:36.428 --> 26:37.595
What was that about?

26:40.432 --> 26:42.851
- Why did he bring you here?
- Did you eat lunch?

26:44.269 --> 26:45.645
What's wrong?

26:47.063 --> 26:48.148
What?

26:49.190 --> 26:50.692
What's wrong with you?

26:55.905 --> 26:58.658
Hey, these things really work.
I couldn't hear a thing.

26:58.742 --> 27:01.369
- What did he say? Did you hear?
- My gosh.

27:28.897 --> 27:32.400
Do you want me to make sure that pervert
won't be able to set foot in the office?

27:32.817 --> 27:34.152
You can't let him have his way.

27:34.861 --> 27:36.780
I definitely won't.

27:36.946 --> 27:38.448
I've become very brave, you know.

27:38.698 --> 27:39.991
I can handle him myself.

27:40.950 --> 27:41.951
With the earplugs?

27:42.535 --> 27:43.370
No.

27:43.828 --> 27:47.082
There's a handsome guy who protects me.

27:49.376 --> 27:50.877
It's rewarding to hear that.

27:51.878 --> 27:53.963
I'm going to see Gyeong-seon later today.

27:54.964 --> 27:55.965
What about me?

27:56.383 --> 27:58.802
She's actually a little mad at me

27:58.885 --> 28:00.345
for putting off hanging out with her.

28:01.137 --> 28:03.223
- Then I'll go with you.
- What?

28:05.266 --> 28:07.268
I can be a good actor. Do you want to bet?

28:07.352 --> 28:08.645
How about we each bet 50,000 won?

28:09.729 --> 28:11.398
Deal.
Then you should get there before I do.

28:11.523 --> 28:12.732
I'll join a bit later.

28:12.816 --> 28:14.651
Look at you.
You have it all mapped out already.

28:15.568 --> 28:16.569
Get going.

28:19.531 --> 28:20.949
Are you crazy? We're at work.

28:22.492 --> 28:24.077
My goodness.

28:48.810 --> 28:50.603
We can just eat out.

28:50.687 --> 28:52.063
Cooking is such a hassle.

28:52.814 --> 28:56.276
Jin-a loves my braised spicy chicken,
you know.

28:56.359 --> 28:58.111
It's been a while since I made it for her.

28:58.987 --> 29:00.071
The date is...

29:01.239 --> 29:03.658
Oh, right.
Were you outside of Seoul recently?

29:04.242 --> 29:06.035
I found a receipt in the car.

29:06.119 --> 29:08.913
It was from Myeoncheon,
the place on the way to Dangjin.

29:10.749 --> 29:13.668
But the date on it was the same day
as when Jin-a was there for work.

29:16.796 --> 29:17.964
I drove her there.

29:19.090 --> 29:21.009
You did? Why?

29:21.676 --> 29:25.138
I was struggling to come up with ideas,
so I wanted to get away for a day,

29:25.430 --> 29:26.973
and I heard she was going there.

29:27.766 --> 29:30.018
But why didn't you tell me?
Jin-a didn't tell me either.

29:30.393 --> 29:31.728
It was nothing important.

29:35.315 --> 29:37.358
You need this too, right?

29:38.318 --> 29:40.445
Who puts cucumbers
in braised spicy chicken?

29:41.112 --> 29:43.156
I guess you're right.

29:44.073 --> 29:45.074
Oh, well.

29:57.378 --> 29:58.505
You're here pretty early.

29:59.005 --> 30:01.299
I am. Where's Gyeong-seon?

30:01.466 --> 30:02.884
I'm here!

30:02.967 --> 30:04.052
Hey.

30:06.387 --> 30:07.555
Are you crazy?

30:09.015 --> 30:10.391
Wait, my leg...

30:15.855 --> 30:17.982
- For my business trip,
- Yes?

30:18.066 --> 30:20.443
he gave me a ride because he wanted
to get away to brainstorm.

30:20.527 --> 30:22.153
And I must say, he's a terrible driver.

30:23.655 --> 30:25.990
This is why you shouldn't be nice
to just anybody.

30:26.533 --> 30:29.285
She's not just anybody.
Jin-a is our family.

30:33.289 --> 30:37.418
I'm going to make sure
that Jin-a meets a guy

30:37.502 --> 30:40.046
who's extremely well-mannered
and faithful.

30:42.257 --> 30:45.176
Look at you. Even just hearing that
makes your heart flutter, right?

30:45.260 --> 30:46.386
Gosh, you're so silly.

30:48.346 --> 30:49.848
I'm not kidding.

30:49.931 --> 30:51.766
There's a guy I've been keeping an eye on.

30:51.933 --> 30:54.561
One of my customers--

30:54.811 --> 30:56.604
How much do you even know
about your customers?

30:57.230 --> 30:59.023
Why are you trying to set her up
with any guy?

30:59.524 --> 31:02.360
Don't think like that. He's been coming
to my store for a long time.

31:02.443 --> 31:04.153
He also has a nice job.

31:05.446 --> 31:07.031
Is that all that matters?

31:07.532 --> 31:08.575
Then I'd qualify too.

31:10.285 --> 31:11.494
We don't consider you a man.

31:11.578 --> 31:12.620
Then am I a woman?

31:13.162 --> 31:16.416
Why are you two bickering at each other
over something so silly?

31:17.250 --> 31:20.587
And just so you know, I don't want
to date anyone for a while.

31:21.087 --> 31:21.921
Why?

31:22.881 --> 31:24.340
Is it because of Gyu-min?

31:24.841 --> 31:27.385
You should just find yourself
a better guy and move on.

31:27.468 --> 31:29.512
- Yes, I know. I know that,
- Gosh.

31:29.596 --> 31:31.973
but I have no interest at the moment.
I'll figure it out.

31:32.223 --> 31:34.392
Sure, whatever. Don't be ridiculous, okay?

31:34.475 --> 31:37.437
I'm going to figure it all out for you
this time, so you just wait.

31:40.481 --> 31:42.108
- Where are you going?
- What's this?

31:42.191 --> 31:43.109
To get more booze.

31:43.443 --> 31:45.528
Bring a lot of booze, okay?

31:48.072 --> 31:50.825
I'll follow him and bring back
a ton of booze.

31:50.909 --> 31:52.577
All right, you smart cookie.

31:55.580 --> 31:56.623
You owe me 50,000 won.

31:58.207 --> 32:01.419
You should've just told her
that we're seeing each other.

32:02.587 --> 32:04.213
I was just so angry.

32:05.173 --> 32:06.215
Already?

32:07.008 --> 32:08.176
Just because of that?

32:09.218 --> 32:10.553
And you tell me to trust you.

32:11.512 --> 32:13.264
Why are you taking it like that?

32:13.598 --> 32:15.224
Then was I supposed to just listen?

32:15.391 --> 32:17.060
She'll set my girlfriend up with...

32:17.644 --> 32:20.188
I mean, how can I tolerate you
going on a date with another guy?

32:20.271 --> 32:21.689
Did I go on a date with another guy?

32:22.065 --> 32:24.067
Did I even say
I will go on a date with him?

32:24.609 --> 32:27.195
She's just saying that.
Why do you take it so seriously?

32:27.278 --> 32:28.947
I don't even want her to talk about it.

32:36.412 --> 32:37.664
Do you like me that much?

32:38.331 --> 32:39.415
Yes.

32:43.169 --> 32:44.379
Seo Jun-hui.

32:46.547 --> 32:48.091
I do trust you.

32:49.258 --> 32:50.677
And I'll always trust you.

32:51.386 --> 32:52.637
So we should...

32:53.596 --> 32:56.349
try not to let little things bother us,
okay?

32:56.432 --> 32:58.309
Be professional, all right?

32:59.644 --> 33:00.603
Okay.

33:04.107 --> 33:07.276
You'd better not be like that
in front of Gyeong-seon ever again.

33:07.360 --> 33:08.528
All right.

33:10.947 --> 33:12.073
You're making it hard for me.

33:16.411 --> 33:17.537
Here's a taxi.

33:19.706 --> 33:21.416
- Get in, Jin-a.
- Okay.

33:25.503 --> 33:27.505
I really enjoyed the dinner today,
Gyeong-seon.

33:27.714 --> 33:29.632
Thanks so much. I'll get going.

33:30.008 --> 33:32.510
- Call me as soon as you get home.
- Okay!

33:33.177 --> 33:34.262
Get home safely.

33:34.470 --> 33:37.181
- Please take her home safely.
- I will.

33:40.393 --> 33:41.519
Let's go.

33:50.361 --> 33:52.030
I have to buy cigarettes.

34:01.789 --> 34:05.501
From now on, don't even suggest
putting on an act or making a bet.

34:05.585 --> 34:07.670
I won't do it
even if the bet is for a million won.

34:08.379 --> 34:11.466
What do you think?
It's no fun because I know that I'll win.

34:11.591 --> 34:13.509
Besides, you won't even give me the money.

34:15.261 --> 34:16.429
Don't laugh.

34:16.763 --> 34:20.016
And what was with the face
when I was getting into the taxi?

34:20.099 --> 34:21.559
Gyeong-seon was watching.

34:22.351 --> 34:23.603
Anyway...

34:26.147 --> 34:27.148
The shortcut?

34:28.483 --> 34:30.026
Why do you want me to get off there?

34:30.818 --> 34:32.070
Where are you now?

34:39.577 --> 34:41.454
Thank you.
I can pay by credit card, right?

34:41.537 --> 34:43.331
Yes, of course.
Would you like your receipt?

34:43.414 --> 34:44.624
No, it's okay.

34:50.088 --> 34:51.255
I just got off the taxi.

34:53.007 --> 34:54.050
Where are you?

35:03.476 --> 35:04.644
You're on your way?

35:17.406 --> 35:21.702
I know I'm pretty, so I get why you're
worried when I go home alone at night,

35:21.786 --> 35:23.371
but you're being overly protective.

35:24.288 --> 35:26.457
I only came to get some exercise
because I ate too much.

35:29.710 --> 35:32.547
Fine, I came
because I wanted to walk with you.

36:03.411 --> 36:05.246
I wanted to have
the first kiss over there.

36:06.330 --> 36:07.707
Who said I'd be okay with that?

36:08.457 --> 36:09.834
I never said it'd be with you.

36:14.297 --> 36:16.841
I was just kidding.
Don't be such an amateur, okay?

36:20.511 --> 36:22.763
That doesn't even hurt
because I'm used to you smacking me.

36:24.682 --> 36:27.435
I did hit you way too many times.

36:28.352 --> 36:29.437
It's fine.

36:32.190 --> 36:34.775
I'll help you become more resilient.

36:37.236 --> 36:38.279
Okay.

37:33.960 --> 37:36.045
You guys are adorable.

37:42.134 --> 37:43.719
Our food is coming.

37:45.846 --> 37:47.056
- Thank you.
- Sure.

38:07.410 --> 38:09.036
- Is it good?
- It's so good.

38:42.486 --> 38:45.781
I LOVE YOU, JIN-A

38:45.865 --> 38:46.949
Hello.

38:51.120 --> 38:52.747
It's for Ms. Yoon Jin-a on the 12th floor.

38:52.830 --> 38:54.665
- Hello.
- I'm here to get my package.

38:54.749 --> 38:57.793
Okay. Can you please fill in this form?

39:01.630 --> 39:02.798
Thank you.

39:07.595 --> 39:09.263
I LOVE YOU, JIN-A.
I'M SORRY. FORGIVE ME.

39:09.347 --> 39:11.390
- He must love her a lot.
- It's so pretty.

39:11.515 --> 39:13.726
Is this why Jin-a's
been acting so different?

39:14.352 --> 39:15.770
- That's disappointing.
- Look at that.

39:15.853 --> 39:17.730
Gosh, Ms. Yoon must be so happy.

39:17.813 --> 39:19.315
When will I ever get one like this?

39:19.648 --> 39:20.775
What is that?

39:27.031 --> 39:30.368
Hey, Jun-hui. I have big news.

39:30.826 --> 39:32.787
You know Jin-a who works downstairs?

39:34.872 --> 39:37.416
Well, you call her by her name as well.

39:37.500 --> 39:40.669
Anyway, I found out
that Ms. Yoon has a boyfriend.

39:43.756 --> 39:46.092
- How do you know that?
- I was in the lobby.

39:47.051 --> 39:48.094
Was it this big?

39:48.677 --> 39:50.846
No, there was a flower bouquet this big.

39:50.930 --> 39:54.058
And it said, "I love you, Jin-a."

39:54.558 --> 39:55.768
Isn't this huge news?

40:03.776 --> 40:04.610
Hey.

40:05.277 --> 40:06.487
Where are you going?

40:07.780 --> 40:08.864
Jun-hui.

40:09.740 --> 40:11.826
Other than what I've gone through today,

40:11.909 --> 40:14.662
there are new rules that need to be kept
at the stores,

40:14.745 --> 40:17.164
so please review the new guideline
thoroughly.

40:17.415 --> 40:19.875
And when you're hiring
new part-time workers,

40:19.959 --> 40:23.546
you need to make sure they come here
and receive the basic training.

40:23.629 --> 40:25.923
If you get caught not doing it,
we'll have to deduct points.

40:26.006 --> 40:27.007
- Okay.
- Okay.

40:27.091 --> 40:28.300
Thank you for your time.

40:28.926 --> 40:30.636
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

40:37.893 --> 40:40.938
Let's eat lunch together
if you don't have any other plans.

40:41.939 --> 40:44.108
I don't feel comfortable
eating with my superior.

40:44.608 --> 40:46.735
- Let's just have some coffee.
- Okay.

40:59.832 --> 41:00.666
Jun-hui.

41:01.500 --> 41:03.586
- Hello.
- What are you doing here?

41:04.086 --> 41:04.920
What?

41:06.046 --> 41:07.298
What are you doing here?

41:07.882 --> 41:09.508
I was here for a training session,

41:09.633 --> 41:11.594
and Ms. Kang wanted
to have some coffee with me.

41:11.719 --> 41:12.553
I see.

41:14.096 --> 41:15.598
Did you two plan this?

41:16.056 --> 41:16.891
Pardon?

41:18.601 --> 41:20.853
No. What are you...

41:20.936 --> 41:22.646
No, not at all.

41:22.730 --> 41:25.608
I really wanted to have some coffee
with you.

41:25.691 --> 41:28.194
I was joking. You took it too seriously.

41:28.986 --> 41:30.946
Hey, how did you know I'd be here?

41:31.030 --> 41:31.906
I didn't know.

41:32.865 --> 41:35.159
I came to ask Jin-a for free coffee,

41:35.242 --> 41:36.869
but I forgot she didn't come
to the office.

41:37.953 --> 41:40.247
Can I get some free coffee with my sister?

41:41.081 --> 41:42.208
Sure.

41:42.958 --> 41:44.043
Yes, of course.

41:46.712 --> 41:48.172
Oh, thank you.

41:48.255 --> 41:49.715
How silly of me.

41:51.800 --> 41:52.843
Come on in.

41:55.221 --> 41:57.723
What's gotten into you?
You rarely ask for favors.

41:57.806 --> 41:59.558
I did what I had to do to get some coffee.

42:01.185 --> 42:02.186
This way, please.

42:06.023 --> 42:06.982
Hello.

42:07.066 --> 42:08.734
- Hello.
- Hello.

42:14.448 --> 42:17.993
- What?
- She's the owner of the Suseo store.

42:19.537 --> 42:20.829
She's Mr. Seo's older sister.

42:22.540 --> 42:24.708
Se-yeong must have started hitting on him.

42:25.584 --> 42:28.003
At this rate, she'll introduce him
to her parents soon.

42:34.260 --> 42:35.886
Take a look at this.

42:41.308 --> 42:45.229
I don't like changing things
including the people around me.

42:47.064 --> 42:48.607
You make it sound like

42:48.691 --> 42:51.694
I called you here to sell some stuff.

42:52.111 --> 42:54.071
They're newly imported machines,

42:54.154 --> 42:57.157
so I just wanted to show them to you
for future reference.

42:58.576 --> 43:01.161
I didn't know you'd be like this
since you're quick-witted.

43:01.245 --> 43:03.747
But you really take jokes seriously.

43:06.250 --> 43:09.295
I'm normally good at taking jokes.

43:09.962 --> 43:13.132
But I guess I don't feel comfortable
around you yet.

43:14.300 --> 43:16.927
Can we meet more often
so that we can become close?

43:21.807 --> 43:22.975
Aren't you here for coffee?

43:25.477 --> 43:27.021
I was thinking about work.

43:28.314 --> 43:30.899
- I think I need to go.
- Already?

43:31.775 --> 43:35.029
You guys can take time
to talk to each other.

43:35.112 --> 43:37.197
We see each other at home all the time.

43:37.281 --> 43:39.783
- You should go.
- Thank you for this.

43:40.200 --> 43:41.368
I'll see you at home.

43:48.208 --> 43:49.543
Let me give you a tip.

43:50.002 --> 43:52.963
Don't ever think he'll be easy to get.

43:55.966 --> 43:57.551
He's not an easy one.

44:05.059 --> 44:06.769
- Do you get it?
- Yes.

44:10.731 --> 44:12.107
Why did you put money inside?

44:12.191 --> 44:14.693
You didn't even break that many cups.
Don't do this again.

44:15.235 --> 44:18.030
No, please take it. I made a mistake.

44:18.113 --> 44:19.823
Just listen to me.

44:19.907 --> 44:21.867
I already feel sorry
for making you work here.

44:21.950 --> 44:24.328
You really don't have to do this
over a small mistake.

44:25.245 --> 44:26.830
You didn't get hurt, right?

44:27.373 --> 44:30.125
- You know how strong I am.
- Yes, I know.

44:31.126 --> 44:32.503
- Hello, sir.
- Hi.

44:32.586 --> 44:35.214
- Ms. Yoon.
- Why did you come all the way here?

44:35.297 --> 44:38.133
You need to head back for our team dinner.
Let's go together.

44:38.384 --> 44:39.843
I'm not going to go.

44:40.386 --> 44:42.805
Why not? Did you really decide
to change yourself?

44:43.347 --> 44:44.932
No, that's not it.

44:45.265 --> 44:46.975
I already have plans for dinner.

44:47.142 --> 44:48.936
Then I'm not going to go either.

44:50.104 --> 44:52.981
I love you, but you sometimes
get on my nerves like this.

44:53.065 --> 44:54.274
You're such a nuisance.

44:54.358 --> 44:56.777
You need to go pick up the flowers anyway.

44:56.860 --> 44:57.945
What flowers?

44:58.779 --> 45:00.781
Didn't you check? I sent you a photo.

45:01.365 --> 45:04.034
Oh, I forgot. You can't use your phone.

45:04.660 --> 45:05.494
Flowers?

45:05.661 --> 45:07.871
Your boyfriend sent you
a huge flower basket.

45:07.996 --> 45:09.164
- My boyfriend?
- Look.

45:10.082 --> 45:11.208
Isn't it pretty?

45:11.708 --> 45:13.293
The employees went wild.

45:13.377 --> 45:14.878
Look. It says, "I love you."

45:20.426 --> 45:21.844
You drove here, right?

45:21.927 --> 45:23.679
What? Ms. Yoon.

45:49.455 --> 45:51.874
It's ready for your approval, sir.

45:55.836 --> 45:58.297
- Where is it?
- It was right here.

47:02.444 --> 47:05.072
I LOVE YOU, JIN-A.
I'M SORRY. FORGIVE ME.

47:13.455 --> 47:15.958
JIN-A, I'M SORRY ABOUT EVERYTHING...

47:20.837 --> 47:22.256
How can I ruin this asshole?

47:23.382 --> 47:24.883
Should I report him as a stalker?

47:30.514 --> 47:31.390
Where does he live?

47:39.273 --> 47:40.107
What's wrong?

47:43.193 --> 47:44.319
Is everyone here?

47:45.862 --> 47:49.157
Mr. Jo is joining our team dinner tonight,
so everyone should come.

47:50.993 --> 47:53.287
Ms. Yoon, did I make myself clear?

47:56.957 --> 47:58.041
Let's go.

47:58.875 --> 48:00.002
Yes, sir.

48:05.507 --> 48:07.134
- All right.
- Let me, sir.

48:08.260 --> 48:10.596
- I'll pour you one, sir.
- It's fine.

48:12.097 --> 48:13.348
Ms. Yoon.

48:14.349 --> 48:15.183
Jin-a.

48:15.934 --> 48:17.019
Excuse me.

48:17.227 --> 48:19.605
- What are you doing? Come over here.
- Excuse me.

48:19.688 --> 48:21.565
Can we get another bottle of soju?

48:21.648 --> 48:24.276
- A bottle of soju?
- And one extra glass, too.

48:28.113 --> 48:30.991
- I'll do it, Mr. Kong.
- Ye-eun, sit down.

48:34.953 --> 48:36.997
Hand it over. I'll do it.

48:38.540 --> 48:39.791
Why are you just sitting there?

48:40.459 --> 48:42.961
Stop it. Don't make a scene
in front of Mr. Jo.

48:45.464 --> 48:48.008
Mr. Jo, I know that I'm being rude.

48:49.217 --> 48:52.012
But I think it's time
we tighten employee discipline.

48:52.179 --> 48:55.307
This isn't a team. There's no sense
of camaraderie among employees.

48:55.891 --> 48:57.267
He's right, sir.

48:57.893 --> 49:00.854
As I have told you before...

49:01.563 --> 49:04.191
an organization should be--

49:04.274 --> 49:05.901
Run properly, I know.

49:07.319 --> 49:09.279
So, what do you suggest we do?

49:09.780 --> 49:12.616
Well, I think...

49:13.575 --> 49:15.494
A gathering like this is an opportunity

49:16.411 --> 49:19.498
to teach them that they should
strictly follow their superiors' orders...

49:20.082 --> 49:21.291
Dong-u.

49:22.501 --> 49:23.627
Yes, Ms. Jeong.

49:27.923 --> 49:29.091
Come and help.

49:29.174 --> 49:31.093
Yes, ma'am.

49:43.397 --> 49:45.816
You are referring
to something like this, right?

49:51.530 --> 49:52.739
Can we get some water?

50:09.047 --> 50:10.716
Gosh, Ms. Jeong.

50:14.928 --> 50:17.097
You've become bolder after acting up once.

50:17.681 --> 50:21.309
I'm sorry. I really have to be somewhere.

50:21.476 --> 50:22.477
Go on.

50:22.728 --> 50:23.729
Ms. Jeong.

50:25.147 --> 50:27.065
- About earlier...
- Save it.

50:27.149 --> 50:29.776
I should thank you
for not acting like you used to do.

50:32.237 --> 50:35.532
Now I realized
that I had been so pathetic.

50:36.241 --> 50:37.659
You really were.

50:39.494 --> 50:41.163
I really do regret being like that.

50:41.788 --> 50:44.416
Thank goodness you came around. Great job.

50:47.335 --> 50:48.462
You're seeing someone, right?

50:49.337 --> 50:50.297
Sorry?

50:50.380 --> 50:51.757
You look prettier these days.

51:09.649 --> 51:11.777
I took him home once when he was drunk.

51:12.152 --> 51:13.612
I don't know if he still lives here.

51:14.654 --> 51:16.323
You must have been really close.

51:16.698 --> 51:18.074
You even took him home.

51:18.533 --> 51:19.701
Do you think I wanted to?

51:19.785 --> 51:21.661
It was because Jin-a insisted.

51:21.745 --> 51:24.498
Don't say anything.
I'm getting even more annoyed.

51:34.424 --> 51:35.425
This is it.

51:37.511 --> 51:40.180
Hey, don't hurt him.

51:41.515 --> 51:43.892
We don't want any trouble.

51:45.185 --> 51:47.312
- Let's talk it out, okay?
- A guest has arrived.

51:57.322 --> 51:58.198
Hey!

52:02.410 --> 52:03.495
Shit.

52:13.755 --> 52:15.298
What the...

52:17.133 --> 52:18.718
He's a real asshole.

52:33.483 --> 52:35.694
What the hell are you doing?

52:36.069 --> 52:38.238
You fucking pervert!

52:48.331 --> 52:49.875
Do you want to die?

52:51.126 --> 52:52.419
I told you to stay away from her!

52:53.003 --> 52:54.462
Why do you care?

52:57.424 --> 52:58.508
Hey!

52:59.134 --> 53:00.135
I'm going to kill you!

53:00.302 --> 53:02.262
I told you to stay the away from her.

53:02.345 --> 53:04.514
Why the hell do you care?

53:09.352 --> 53:10.228
Hey.

53:11.605 --> 53:12.647
Go ahead and report us

53:13.648 --> 53:15.734
for trespassing and property damage.

53:16.401 --> 53:19.779
Then I'll put you in jail for all those
on top of stalking and sexual assault.

53:21.406 --> 53:23.491
What? Sexual assault?

53:24.242 --> 53:26.286
- What did you do to my sister?
- Wait.

53:26.369 --> 53:27.871
Seung-ho, I can explain.

53:27.954 --> 53:29.706
Go ahead and report me for this,
you asshole!

53:55.732 --> 53:56.566
Are you okay?

53:58.568 --> 54:00.153
It just grazed me.

54:01.196 --> 54:02.572
What was that about sexual assault?

54:03.531 --> 54:05.075
Was Jin-a really harassed?

54:06.826 --> 54:08.703
He caused a scene at the store.

54:09.579 --> 54:10.622
Isn't it obvious?

54:12.082 --> 54:14.209
That little shit.

54:14.668 --> 54:16.711
Shouldn't we report him to the police?

54:16.878 --> 54:18.672
What if this happens again?

54:22.509 --> 54:23.468
It shouldn't.

54:23.551 --> 54:25.220
How can we make sure it doesn't?

54:25.553 --> 54:28.264
I barely made time today.
I have to get back right away.

54:29.265 --> 54:30.350
I'll take care of it.

54:30.433 --> 54:32.811
Hey. You have work to do too.

54:34.145 --> 54:36.314
Gosh, Jin-a is giving me a headache.

54:38.441 --> 54:39.693
Hey, don't do it.

54:40.276 --> 54:42.487
Why not? I should tell her to get a grip.

54:44.823 --> 54:47.784
There's someone else to blame for this.
Why would you get mad at her?

54:50.745 --> 54:51.871
Don't let her know of this.

54:52.706 --> 54:54.249
You'll stress her out if you do.

54:57.085 --> 54:58.169
Okay?

55:01.047 --> 55:02.173
Do you understand?

55:04.467 --> 55:06.594
You act like you are her little brother.

55:09.514 --> 55:12.642
Jin-a shouldn't date anyone
since all she does is getting in trouble.

55:13.309 --> 55:14.436
Damn it.

56:45.985 --> 56:48.363
Gyeong-seon, where are you?

56:49.739 --> 56:52.784
Oh, you're home? What are you doing?

56:54.244 --> 56:55.620
You're drinking? With whom?

56:56.121 --> 56:57.455
Alone.

56:58.414 --> 56:59.707
Why? Do you want to come?

57:00.834 --> 57:04.337
Do you miss me already?

57:10.009 --> 57:11.052
Yes.

57:11.970 --> 57:14.305
I'm going to steal some beer
from Jun-hui's place.

57:14.556 --> 57:15.431
Yes.

57:16.599 --> 57:18.435
You can come too if you want.

57:32.866 --> 57:33.950
What?

57:35.535 --> 57:36.995
Talk louder.

57:37.829 --> 57:38.663
What?

57:39.706 --> 57:41.666
Where are you calling from?

57:43.710 --> 57:45.670
I'm still working.

57:46.921 --> 57:48.548
I'm at work.

57:49.757 --> 57:50.967
You're at the office?

57:51.843 --> 57:55.472
Gosh, why are you working until so late?

57:56.681 --> 57:58.683
But then again, it's not just you.

58:00.518 --> 58:03.980
I'm not even sure if he is not back yet
or went back out.

58:05.899 --> 58:08.568
He always tells me
that he works until late.

58:08.902 --> 58:10.945
I think he's dating someone in secret.

58:12.071 --> 58:14.908
Have you not noticed
something different about him?

58:18.411 --> 58:19.454
Hello?

58:20.538 --> 58:21.623
Hello?

58:22.749 --> 58:23.875
Jin-a?

58:25.418 --> 58:26.419
Jin-a?

59:06.584 --> 59:08.378
Where are you? Are you busy?

59:08.878 --> 59:10.213
You're not picking up.

59:10.588 --> 59:12.340
Why aren't you picking up?

59:12.423 --> 59:13.841
Can you answer my call?

59:14.968 --> 59:16.636
I'll go to your place.

59:47.709 --> 59:49.127
Is someone chasing you?

59:49.544 --> 59:50.878
What are you doing at my place?

59:51.421 --> 59:52.505
Your place?

59:54.632 --> 59:55.842
Your place is my place.

59:57.552 --> 59:58.928
I'm tired. Please leave.

59:59.012 --> 01:00:01.222
Let me finish my beer. Let go of me.

01:00:02.974 --> 01:00:04.809
Just take that home.

01:00:06.936 --> 01:00:09.105
Take this one too.
Drink up and sleep tight.

01:00:09.314 --> 01:00:11.691
No, I'm just going to finish this.

01:00:12.859 --> 01:00:13.776
Go on.

01:00:13.901 --> 01:00:17.905
Can I please go after I finish this?

01:00:18.156 --> 01:00:19.282
Please, my brother?

01:00:21.034 --> 01:00:22.493
Okay, fine.

01:00:22.577 --> 01:00:25.496
I don't know what you're angry about,
but don't take it out on me.

01:00:25.580 --> 01:00:26.998
I'm going to kill you tomorrow.

01:00:29.167 --> 01:00:31.252
You are so mean. My gosh.

01:00:33.254 --> 01:00:34.756
Bye. Good night.

01:00:59.656 --> 01:01:00.865
You can come out now.

01:01:06.162 --> 01:01:07.288
What's wrong?

01:01:13.169 --> 01:01:15.171
Why are you crying?

01:01:15.880 --> 01:01:16.923
What's--

01:01:17.006 --> 01:01:19.342
I can't stand up
because I have a foot cramp.

01:01:25.056 --> 01:01:26.057
Oh, gosh.

01:01:26.933 --> 01:01:27.934
Come here.

01:01:33.147 --> 01:01:34.232
Oh, no.

01:01:39.487 --> 01:01:41.489
What took you so long?

01:01:41.739 --> 01:01:43.116
I'm sorry. I really am.

01:01:45.660 --> 01:01:46.744
I'm sorry.

01:01:49.497 --> 01:01:50.498
My gosh.

01:01:59.006 --> 01:02:01.467
You should've gone home.
Why did you come here?

01:02:02.051 --> 01:02:03.344
Did you miss me that much?

01:02:04.929 --> 01:02:07.807
I checked the security footage.

01:02:13.062 --> 01:02:14.939
What did you do with the flowers?

01:02:17.608 --> 01:02:18.818
I threw them away.

01:02:19.944 --> 01:02:22.238
You threw them away? Where?

01:02:24.031 --> 01:02:26.159
Why? Do you want them?

01:02:28.703 --> 01:02:31.539
Yes, I want them so badly.

01:02:39.338 --> 01:02:42.258
I thought you'd only be bothered by it,
so I just threw them out.

01:02:43.634 --> 01:02:44.844
And I figured you'd understand.

01:02:47.889 --> 01:02:49.682
I do understand.

01:02:50.141 --> 01:02:51.642
And I'm also grateful.

01:02:53.019 --> 01:02:56.105
But I don't want to bother you
with something like that either.

01:02:56.856 --> 01:02:58.858
It's better to take care of it on my own.

01:02:59.609 --> 01:03:01.819
It only ended up bothering you again.

01:03:03.237 --> 01:03:04.614
It doesn't bother me.

01:03:06.365 --> 01:03:08.242
After all, you're here with me.

01:03:10.036 --> 01:03:12.371
Then why didn't you pick up the phone
all day?

01:03:12.789 --> 01:03:14.040
You were out of touch.

01:03:16.125 --> 01:03:18.169
I had a busy day at work.

01:03:19.170 --> 01:03:22.131
Next time, I'll let you know beforehand.

01:03:22.799 --> 01:03:24.342
You'd better do that.

01:03:24.926 --> 01:03:27.386
Otherwise, I'm going to take revenge
and just disappear.

01:03:32.016 --> 01:03:33.184
And hide in my closet again?

01:03:34.227 --> 01:03:37.063
You should hang yourself
on a hanger next time.

01:03:37.230 --> 01:03:38.439
I bet no one will notice.

01:03:39.315 --> 01:03:40.858
You're so mean.

01:03:50.701 --> 01:03:51.786
Come here.

01:04:00.670 --> 01:04:02.255
Don't ever hide like that again.

01:04:03.089 --> 01:04:04.549
I felt so sorry.

01:04:07.051 --> 01:04:08.761
I had nowhere else to hide.

01:04:11.222 --> 01:04:13.307
I'll make sure
you never have to hide again.

01:04:13.641 --> 01:04:14.475
I promise.

01:04:55.683 --> 01:04:57.727
- Are you doing it right?
- I am.

01:05:11.032 --> 01:05:12.116
Let me see.

01:05:14.327 --> 01:05:16.245
What is this?

01:05:16.329 --> 01:05:17.163
What?

01:05:17.246 --> 01:05:19.498
I'm going to do it myself.

01:05:25.338 --> 01:05:26.964
My, that's really pretty.

01:05:29.133 --> 01:05:30.426
You look so cute now.

01:06:55.678 --> 01:06:56.721
Oh, no.

01:06:59.515 --> 01:07:00.850
Where are my clothes?

01:07:02.184 --> 01:07:04.228
Oh, gosh. What time is it now?

01:07:04.311 --> 01:07:05.938
What? Hang on.

01:07:09.942 --> 01:07:12.069
Where did it go?
Why didn't the alarm go off?

01:07:12.153 --> 01:07:13.195
Hold on.

01:08:15.216 --> 01:08:16.258
Dad.

01:08:18.385 --> 01:08:20.221
Did you go out to exercise?

01:08:23.724 --> 01:08:24.767
Yes.

01:08:30.815 --> 01:08:31.816
Jin-a.

01:08:34.318 --> 01:08:36.112
I want you to...

01:08:44.203 --> 01:08:45.663
I lied.

01:09:22.449 --> 01:09:25.703
I want to let the world know
that you're mine because you're so pretty.

01:09:26.287 --> 01:09:29.206
I'll turn 40 soon.

01:09:29.999 --> 01:09:32.710
List ten reasons why you like me.

01:09:32.793 --> 01:09:35.713
I like you because it's you.
There are no other reasons.

01:09:35.796 --> 01:09:36.922
My gosh!

01:09:37.381 --> 01:09:40.342
Those who date secretly
always make it more obvious.

01:09:40.426 --> 01:09:42.553
What's wrong?
Are you also guilty of something?

01:09:42.636 --> 01:09:43.971
Only the victim would know.

01:09:44.555 --> 01:09:47.224
We should be careful?
We didn't even do anything.

01:09:47.308 --> 01:09:48.392
What the heck is going on?

01:09:48.475 --> 01:09:50.227
What is it? What happened?

01:09:50.311 --> 01:09:52.313
- Jun-hui saw this?
- Let go of me!

01:09:52.396 --> 01:09:56.400
- What is it?
- Gyeong-seon will probably go berserk.

01:09:56.483 --> 01:09:59.820
- Well, I think she's seeing someone.
- Yes?

01:09:59.904 --> 01:10:00.779
Really?

01:10:00.863 --> 01:10:03.699
Until when do we have to keep it
from everyone? We should just--

01:10:04.116 --> 01:10:07.203
For just a little longer.
Let's wait just a bit longer.

01:10:08.787 --> 01:10:10.956
Subtitle translation by Lee Ja-won
